  <section>
    <title>How to use it ?</title>
    <screen language="shell">$ openstack optimize audittemplate create \
  at1 airflow_optimization --strategy uniform_airflow

$ openstack optimize audit create -a at1 -p threshold_airflow=410 \
       -p threshold_inlet_t=29.0 -p threshold_power=355.0 -p period=310</screen>
